title: Bill Minns Rotunda honours half a century of community spirit (Casey City Council)
text: ( Source : Casey City Council ) Issued Thursday 22 October 2015 In recognition of more than five decades of community participation, a rotunda at Pioneers Park has been named in honour of Berwick local Bill Minns. City of Casey Mayor Cr Mick
